vpp-snmp-agent-v2 (2.2.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * VPP 25.06 compatibility release
  * Fixed stats interface collection for VPP 25.06-rc2
  * Added safe stats path access with fallback to default values
  * Improved bonding interface speed calculation as sum of active members
  * Uses VPP sw_interface_bond_dump and sw_interface_slave_dump APIs
  * Correctly reports aggregate speed for multi-member bonds
  * Handles missing optional stats paths gracefully
  * Better error logging for troubleshooting
  * Compatible with both older and newer VPP versions

 -- VPP Team <vpp@example.com>  Tue, 09 Dec 2025 15:00:00 +0000

vpp-snmp-agent-v2 (2.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Critical fix: Bonding interface speed aggregation
  * Fix case-insensitive interface name matching (BondEthernet0)
  * Correct speed calculation: sum of all active member speeds
  * Multi-strategy member detection (attribute, naming, fallback)
  * Debug logging for interface detection and aggregation
  * Support for LACP bonding with dynamic member failover
  * Verified with 2x100Gbps HundredGigabit Ethernet ports
  * SNMP OID 1.3.6.1.2.1.31.1.1.1.15.N correctly reports aggregate speed

 -- VPP Team <vpp@example.com>  Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:00:00 +0000
